{"tid":2026076,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(周梓樂案)律政司去信岑敖暉恐嚇7日內撤文 岑：Noted with thanks","createTime":"2020-05-20T16:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T17:06:12.000Z","uid":125168,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d27f63dc75ec46c4085bac6604a47b0fa3943eb0","tid":2026076,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:51:58.000Z","msg":"【抗暴之戰】岑敖暉撰文指控警方謀殺周梓樂 律政司去信恐嚇7日內撤文<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200520/XDQBFUCE7NQRTEAWPBSCXSQRME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FXDQBFUCE7NQRTEAWPBSCXSQRME%2F&d=JWMo9xAWlgSpyjxIujWPsSfe5Xzx4ME6JwL9AZsFK0I%3D&h=f20c597c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FXDQBFUCE7NQRTEAWPBSCXSQRME%2F&h=20f58e66\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200520/XDQBFUCE7NQRTEAWPBSCXSQRME/</a><br />\n<br />\n荃灣區議員岑敖暉月初在facebook及《香港獨立媒體網》以「周梓樂被香港警察謀殺身亡，半年」為題撰文，批評警方於周梓樂去世當晚阻礙救援，懷疑周梓樂是被警方所謀殺。繼警方早前發信批文章誣蔑警隊，律政司周三（20日）亦向岑發信，質疑他違反臨時禁制令，要求他在7日內撤走文章。岑以「Noted with thanks.（知悉，謝謝）」回應，並表明不會移除文章。"},{"pid":"e1d2a20afd68954e76107047dfe9d9c31f1c0350","tid":2026076,"uid":231583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T16:53:08.000Z","msg":"律政司的信中提及，高等法院去年底頒佈臨時禁制令，禁止任何人在網上發佈或轉發鼓勵或煽動使用暴力的信息，而岑的文章或涉「促進、鼓勵或煽動暴力」，質疑文章違反法庭禁制令，要求他在7天內移除該文章。<br />\n<br />\n以言入罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017498ed9589687253de1fc7524201c0ca529bd3","tid":2026076,"uid":224657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"e91d2a46099f88fab1079da1c5d52af04329cac9","tid":2026076,"uid":155773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"夠料就即拉la<br />\n出警告信即係唔夠料？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;懷疑&rdquo;都唔比用咩"}]}